<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;">金秋十月开新篇，秋高气爽启新程。</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">10月27日，江西软件职业技术大学井冈山校区揭牌仪式、中国民办教育协会职业本科教育专委会成立仪式、先锋软件集团30周年和江西软件职业技术大学20周年“双庆”典礼，在江西软件职业技术大学井冈山校区盛大开幕。150余名政府单位、行业协会、省内外高校、媒体等领导和嘉宾莅临活动现场。广大校友、家长、社会人士和在校2万余名师生通过线上线下参加仪式。100余家政府单位、行业协会、省内外高校、校友会等发来贺信、贺礼以及嘉宾现场致辞表示祝福。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1734411620327.png" alt="1734411620327.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1734411620327.png" style=""><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1734411806982.png" alt="1734411806982.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1734411806982.png" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-28%2016%3A05%3A08ZZZ9475.JPG?Expires=2045462709&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=sGxVgSjQaJPzZFzKEGghHQuJc8I%3D" alt="Image 3 of 21" data-href="" style=""></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">产教融合，驭时而进。井冈山校区的揭牌，具有里程碑式的意义，作为井冈山市家门口的第一所本科高校，将为职教人才培育和革命老区振兴同步发展画出最大“同心圆”。典礼现场，数字经济产业园入园企业授牌仪式、吉安电子信息产业人才就业基地授牌仪式、南昌大学等四方签约仪式、吉安职业技术学院等四方签约仪式、江西软件职业技术大学与7家企业签约仪式等，是学校“校企融合、产学互动”办学模式生动写照。此次盛典，还专门举行了中国民办教育协会职业本科教育专委会成立仪式，这标志着职业本科教育发展进入新的阶段，也将推动职业本科教育的高质量发展，为教育强国建设贡献力量。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1734411832806.png" alt="1734411832806.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1734411832806.png" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-28%2014%3A49%3A47%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20241028144805.jpg?Expires=2045458187&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=2awskW0yEYY5J4MAzGPl8mwu154%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-28%2016%3A08%3A00b1.JPG?Expires=2045462881&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=ruxaziCvcXGidfMWVRXWUCP6gyQ%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-28%2016%3A08%3A1662.JPG?Expires=2045462896&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=SzHLaPD%2BGLYscXxOMg5o9sXYz%2FQ%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A27%3A04A1.jpg?Expires=2045525224&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=qWn5yWx4dDwDuyr%2FomTzXdNqPBY%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A27%3A41A2.jpg?Expires=2045525262&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=jUMv%2BSSa%2BEgOLY5qbp5whyxVuSg%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A29%3A03A3.jpg?Expires=2045525343&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=dhKqdy%2Fc7EkcWg7h34cNPH9q07o%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A32%3A20A4.jpg?Expires=2045525540&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=uCSf4%2FGHr8wmbNfkVlPfkvxyAPw%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A33%3A51A5.jpg?Expires=2045525631&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=8wg4kb9vIyVH7%2Brp2JPR0%2FnPu3s%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A34%3A37A6.jpg?Expires=2045525677&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=w%2FC4IiOHHre%2FJ2vtKjWE7nuLyOE%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A35%3A17A7.jpg?Expires=2045525718&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=eHnvuRIeUeEQXYbC%2FAmVfNwarYs%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-28%2021%3A06%3A0533.JPG?Expires=2045480765&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=OcFtgncgpbBQLhFpX71GrAt8dOM%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">构建区块链生态圈，探索新质生产力，先锋以数字经济聚“势”、未来产业谋“远”。活动当天，区块链、数字经济成为最热门的话题，在2024中国软件井冈山先锋主论坛上，《支持大模型训练和推理的自主可控的基础设施》《区块链与区块链服务网络(BSN)》等主题报告吸引了广大参会者。在新时代人才培养与经济社会发展论坛、新时代信创产业发展趋势论坛、区块链技术与人才培养新模式论坛、井冈山江西软件职业技术大学校友论坛等4个平行论坛上，专家学者们纷纷围绕区块链、数字经济、职业教育、人才培养等多个角度进行研讨交流，展望未来。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1734411951500.png" alt="1734411951500.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1734411951500.png" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A45%3A242341.jpg?Expires=2045526324&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=D2%2Br23tR%2BBPf07lK3JLkp4yPyzI%3D" alt="Image 17 of 21" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A49%3A51532.jpg?Expires=2045526591&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=E907wUgkisi8t%2B0b6%2FxHV%2FpFYBc%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A51%3A3874.jpg?Expires=2045526699&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=5y8X474l1W9TyOJ60iU5z6NMsCA%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A52%3A10542.jpg?Expires=2045526731&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=rcL2tfJJP0HS8NGTkk5ptSiknhY%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-10-29%2009%3A58%3A01544.jpg?Expires=2045527082&amp;OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&amp;Signature=JY65urXPhGzG8rtdWLgpNDZDRbA%3D" alt="" data-href="" style=""></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;">砥砺日新，弦歌不辍。三十年软件先锋</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">，坚守国产软件，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;">二十载职教示范</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">，培育时代匠人。</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;">展望未来，集团和学校将继续秉承井冈山精神，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">聚焦区块链、数字经济、职业教育、人才培养，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;">坚持创新驱动，加强技术研发，推动产业升级，努力培养更多高素质高层次技术技能人才，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">努力建设有特色、有品质、 有情怀、有作为的高水平职业技术大学，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;">为实现中国式现代化和教育强国贡献先锋力量。</span></p>